PrognosAI: AI-Driven Predictive Maintenance System Using Time-Series Sensor Data

ðŸ“Œ Project Objective
PrognosAI is an AI-based predictive maintenance system designed to estimate the Remaining Useful Life (RUL) of industrial machinery using multivariate time-series sensor data. Built on the NASA CMAPSS dataset, this project aims to:
Enable timely maintenance decisions
Reduce unplanned downtime
Optimize asset utilization
It leverages deep learning models like LSTM/GRU to detect sequential degradation patterns and forecast failures across domains such as turbines, pumps, and motors.

